37285>>>    // not set the Server property or send ADDOStructure. We will simply use
37285>>>    // DDO's to mine data and generate HTML for our cWebHTMLBox objects.
37285>>>    // It is the HTML in these objects that is sent to the client each time 
37285>>>    // this page is shown.
